## Erlang VM args for the session-manager release.
##
## The release boot scripts require a node name even though we do not rely on
## Erlang distribution (the service is reached over gRPC). Binding the node to
## 127.0.0.1 keeps the distribution port loopback-only inside the container.
-name session_manager@127.0.0.1
-setcookie acg_session_manager

## Kernel poll and async threads for I/O-heavy serving.
+K true
+A 30
